    "type": "message",
    "text": "Today with <@U01DWJSAF2B> we are officially launching the Early Access of our book *WebAssembly from the Ground Up:* <https://wasmgroundup.com/>\n\nWe decided to go \"digital first\" to support features like interactive inspectors, code highlight on hover, REPLs for examples and other ideas from the Explorable Explanation world.\n\nThe book explores the fundamentals of WebAssembly by building a compiler for a simple programming language step by step using JavaScript and <https://ohmjs.org/|OhmJS>\n\nWe would love to get your feedback!",
